mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector

Class VectorDataStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.accumulo.AccumuloDataStore
      • mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.VectorDataStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataStore

    public class VectorDataStore
extends AccumuloDataStore
    This is the most convenient way of using GeoWave as a SimpleFeature persistence store backed by Accumulo. Beyond the basic functions of AccumuloDataStore (general-purpose query and ingest of any data adapter type) this class enables distributed rendering and decimation on SimpleFeature, both with CQL filtering able to be applied to features on the tablet server.
